": "mp4", "protocol": "https", "resolution": "1080x1920", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/90.0.4430.70 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "format_id": "9", "format": "9 - 1080x1920"}, {"format_id": "dash-2031974964017932v", "ext": "mp4", "width": 1080, "height": 1920, "tbr": 1853.473, "format_note": "DASH video", "container": "mp4_dash", "vcodec": "vp09.00.40.08.00.01.01.01.00", "acodec": "none", "dynamic_range": "SDR", "url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQPcv2SNxwiJhI7bbFTuTukukH8Oh6QK1OxxXm9RqOOoCKl86EgfPTjxc6cOpYB9XE3HFx24krkW1IFgTL8GpmqUEa72AcLrgsxm1nk.mp4?_nc_cat=111&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=XCzzsa1Ep2AQ7kNvwG5m2jZ&%3D&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=bgTsb4QldONYQnYGeroXBw&_nc_zt=28&_nc_ss=7a32e&oh=00_Af3JtT1WF3JUz6c5bhYDSzJ5kN10OBUA35XNsy6j5vGdbg&oe=69D7B25C", "manifest_stream_number": 0, "is_dash_periods": true, "protocol": "https", "resolution": "1080x1920", "aspect_ratio": 0.56, "filesize_approx": 17337618, "http_headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/90.0.4430.70 Safari/537.36", "Accept": "text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8", "Accept-Language": "en-us,en;q=0.5", "Sec-Fetch-Mode": "navigate", "Referer": "https://www.instagram.com/"}, "video_ext": "mp4", "audio_ext": "none", "abr": 0, "vbr": 1853.473, "format": "dash-2031974964017932v - 1080x1920 (DASH video)"}], "title": "Video by cristophergeilermd", "description": "🧬Your body already makes its own longevity molecule. After 40, you’re running out of it. 🧬Alpha-ketoglutarate (AKG) is a metabolite your mitochondria produce as part of the Krebs cycle. It’s not a drug. It’s not synthetic. But its mechanism of action on aging biology is extraordinary.Here’s what it does simultaneously:\n🔴 Inhibits mTOR - the chronic activation of this growth-signaling pathway is one of the primary drivers of cellular aging. AKG puts the brakes on it.\n🔵 Rewrites your epigenome - AKG is a required cofactor for TET demethylases and histone demethylases (KDMs), the enzymes that regulate which genes get silenced as you age. It directly modulates H3K9me3 and H3K27me3 marks.\n🟢 Mimics caloric restriction - AKG levels naturally rise with fasting, exercise, and dietary restriction. In a landmark 2020 study in Cell Metabolism, aging mice given supplemental calcium-AKG lived longer, showed significantly less frailty, had lower systemic inflammatory cytokines, and demonstrated what the authors called a compression of morbidity - more life, but critically, healthier life. 🐭. The ABLE Trial - a double-blind, placebo-controlled RCT currently underway - is now testing 1g of sustained-release Ca-AKG versus placebo in 120 adults aged 40-60, with DNA methylation age as the primary endpoint. 📚 References:Asadi Shahmirzadi A, et al. Alpha-Ketoglutarate, an Endogenous Metabolite, Extends Lifespan and Compresses Morbidity in Aging Mice. Cell Metabolism. 2020;32(3):447-456. doi:10.1016/j.cmet.2020.08.004Chin RM, et al. The metabolite α-ketoglutarate extends lifespan by inhibiting ATP synthase and TOR. Nature. 2014;510:397-401. doi:10.1038/nature13264\nSandalova E, et al. Alpha-ketoglutarate supplementation and BiologicaL agE in middle-aged adults (ABLE) - intervention study protocol. GeroScience. 2023;45:2897-2907. doi:10.1007/s11357-023 Bayliak MM, Lushchak VI. Mimicking caloric restriction for anti-aging effects: The pro-oxidant role of alpha-ketoglutarate. Advances in Protein Chemistry and Structural Biology. 2022. #AlphaKetoglutarate #AKG #CaAKG #LongevityScience #LongevityMedicine", "duration": 74.833, "timestamp": 1774994955, "uploader_id": "6101673647", "uploader": "Cristopher Geiler MD", "channel": "cristophergeilermd", "like_count": 374, "comment_count": 5, "comments": [{"author": "metaversematt00", "author_id": "6362034765", "id": "17924191581099993", "text": "Interestingly, the lifespan extension effect was only observed in female mice, while both male and female mice demonstrated a strong reduction in lifetime frailty", "timestamp": 1775346425}, {"author": "blacquecondor", "author_id": "66881748403", "id": "18065832392681212", "text": "L Ornithine Alpha Ketoglutarate..?", "timestamp": 1775135336}, {"author": "arthurdavis1141", "author_id": "3764952747", "id": "17969833269013975", "text": "I have a doctor crush on him.", "timestamp": 1775129663}, {"author": "cristophergeilermd", "author_id": "6101673647", "id": "18576481606050392", "text": "It is not studied as much", "timestamp": 1775095771}, {"author": "loveforeverfun", "author_id": "10460079764", "id": "17941068918012363", "text": "Only Calcium AKG C-AKG not Arganine AKG A-Akg", "timestamp": 1775082582}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/658127069_26043819075287586_6325949438546610425_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p640x640_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMDgweDE5MjEuc2RyLmY3MTg3OC41OTFjNTQ4MDY1MDJkY2RjMjkwNjRiYmEyOGM5ZGFmMGZjZmMyZjQ0ZTlmYjI5YzI4YTlmMWIzZGJiMDMxYWMxMS5jMiJ9&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=106&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGykVQcHdXHsx1hsmKoy1uXf9aHAdNtRxVXUj-tZr8a-1T78-VFEzSjk-Z290kl7zk&_nc_ohc=jfrltjD8ZXIQ7kNvwGl7kxa&_nc_gid=bgTsb4QldONYQnYGeroXBw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af33-HEbDbSGbZw9z3c8OSxhdME1z14gzo1wEvCGXXsKHA&oe=69D7A5E3&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1137, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1137"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/658127069_26043819075287586_6325949438546610425_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p750x750_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMDgweDE5MjEuc2RyLmY3MTg3OC41